msgstr ":func:`X(i)<qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.X>` - Pauli X actuando sobre el cúbit *i*"

#: ../../modules/analog/analog.rst:29
msgid ":func:`Y(i)<qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.Y>` - Pauli Y acting on qubit *i*"
msgstr ":func:`Y(i)<qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.Y>` - Pauli Y actuando sobre el cúbit *i*"

#: ../../modules/analog/analog.rst:30
msgid ":func:`Z(i)<qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.Z>` - Pauli Z acting on qubit *i*"
msgstr ":func:`Z(i)<qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.Z>` - Pauli Z actuando sobre el cúbit *i*"

#: ../../modules/analog/analog.rst:31
msgid ":func:`I(i)<qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.I>` - Identity acting on qubit *i*"
msgstr ":func:`I(i)<qilisdk.analog.hamiltonian.I>` - Identidad actuando sobre el cúbit *i*"

